{
  "stem": "11179.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And you wanted to hear a third side, there were the Russians, which all was broadcast in English, and I believe in German too at one time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I can't swear by that-- certainly in English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then there were the Japanese stations who also had English broadcast.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I think we got a cross cut.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And strangely enough, most of them weren't lying too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It wouldn't have made sense because there was-- now, the commentary, it was different.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I'm talking about the news reporting directly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Now, the commentary was of course-- the German commentary was certainly different than the commentary you heard from English American stations even-- even though America was not involved.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I-- I would say we were well informed what was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "What we were not not too well-informed was about the concentration camp, and what's going on in-- in Germany and in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were not too well-informed of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There were rumors only.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were not informed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But about the general world we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Because of the competition, they were all in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You see, we were not the only listeners there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "There were about 3,000 to 4,000 Germans living there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There were about 25,000 Russians living there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "There were about 4,000 Russian Jews living there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So-- and-- and and there were a number of thousands at that time still American and British subjects living there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So-- and French people, by all means.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They had their own concessions there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they a fantastic-- I-- I forgot his name-- fantastic narrator on the radio, also in German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And so we got a cross cut.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And to say we were not informed is totally misleading.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We heard what was going on in the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew pretty well what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
